*[[Oromë]] discovers the [[Elves]] near the shores of [[Sea of Helcar|Helcar]]; he names them the Eldar, the People of the Stars. As a result of [[Morgoth|Melkor]]'s spies and whispers, some Eldar are afraid of Oromë and flee as he approaches.<ref name="Annals">{{MR|P2e}}, pp. 72-4</ref>
*About this time, it is possible that the first [[Orcs]] are created, being corrupted from Elves.<ref name="Annals" />
